snippet.title: JOHNNY DEPP Inspired Me To Support Victims! Starting A Project
snippet.description:
Covering the horrible situation Johnny Depp has gone through with Ex-Wife Amber Heard inspired me to start a big project to support male victims of DV.

Join me discussing what is involved and what needs to be done to create support for men.

PODCAST CHANNEL - https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzfdg2qzHOy5p0EK6jEJJfA

PODCAST - https://linktr.ee/DissentIntoTheWormhole

Contact me - https://linktr.ee/steviejraw

Join this channel to get access to perks:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCAk03rcNVtLK1_LlgRTOh2w/join

Help me open a Domestic Violence Shelter For Men -
https://igg.me/at/steviejsrefugeformen/x/26939005#/

TubeBuddy - https://www.tubebuddy.com/StevieJReviews 

Art Of Elysium Donation Page - https://www.pledge.to/the-art-of-elysium

Aventino Watches - 15% Discount Code (stevie_j_raw15)
Aventino Website - https://aventinowatches.com/collections/all

Have an awesome day!

THANKS FOR WATCHING!!
#JusticeForJohnnyDepp #JohnnyDepp #DeppHeard
